                <div class="pl col-time">
                  <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37662893/#comments">回应</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;
                  2016-04-27 17:28
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="37662885">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2433432/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2433432-4.jpg" alt="The Capital M" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37662885/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/37662885/" class="">第368页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2433432/" class=" " title="The Capital M">The Capital M</a>
                (得失寸心知)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="37662885">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">不改变购买力的分配，粮食增产和持续饥馑之间的鸿沟是难以填平的。改变分配制度的问题恰恰是基金会解决不了而且有意不涉及的问题。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-04-27 17:25</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                不改变购买力的分配，粮食增产和持续饥馑之间的鸿沟是难以填平的。改变分配制度的问题恰恰是基金会解决不了而且有意不涉及的问题。
